item.description:
IBM Engineering Lifecycle Management (ELM) Expertise

Technical consultancy and custom development for your lifecycle management tools.

  • DNG Extensions: Development of OpenSocial widgets for IBM Engineering Requirements Management (DOORS Next).
  • EWM Plugins: Java-based automation and extensions for IBM Engineering Workflow Management (formerly RTC).
  • OSLC Architecture: Tool integration and interoperability solutions.
